## Generic Object Example

{
  _id: <serial:UUID>,
  type: <string:template/type>,
  geometry: <GeoJSON>,
  name: <string>,
  properties: <object:fields>,
  connections: <object:type_connections>,
  permissions: <object:user_permissions>,
}


## Usage: USER (e.g., Joshua Powell, R. John Dawes)

{
  _id: 'bl124klwerjsflkj3',
  type: 'user',
  geometry: <GeoJSON>,
  name: 'R. John Dawes',
  properties: <object:fields>,
  connections: <object:type_connections>,
  permissions: {
    {
      _id: 'm34u4nsfjkwjk4lk4j',
      view: 1,
      edit: 1,
      delete: 1,
      create: 0, 
    },
    {
      _id: 'q4jdfui4nf8dj48df',
      view: 1,
      edit: 1,
      delete: 1,
      create: 1, 
    }

  },
}


## Usage: RESOURCE (e.g., Single Activity Report Instance, Single NFWF Site/BMP/Project/Metric, Single Conservation Project)

{
  _id: 'm34u4nsfjkwjk4lk4j',
  type: 'activity_report',
  geometry: <GeoJSON>,
  name: 'Activity Report',
  properties: <object:fields>,
  connections: <object:type_connections>,
  permissions: <object:user_permissions>,
}


